    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1-3 人在线合作</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c32961d2084078bb2e1c6d3f206f7180.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c32961d2084078bb2e1c6d3f206f7180.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/c32961d2084078bb2e1c6d3f206f7180.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>HOLY PURGE 是一款最多可容纳 3 名玩家的合作恐怖生存游戏。<br>在这个在线合作体验中扮演神圣的牧师，你必须共同努力阻止邪恶的瘟疫降临中世纪的村庄。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神圣的弟兄们</h2>探索一个被邪恶困扰的开放世界中世纪村庄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/9dd3e0308266a4a688716f61f456f0ad.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/9dd3e0308266a4a688716f61f456f0ad.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/9dd3e0308266a4a688716f61f456f0ad.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收集仪式物品以逆转女巫咒语。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/6bcd2ba8cf82aa352fca5e5a0fd34122.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/6bcd2ba8cf82aa352fca5e5a0fd34122.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/6bcd2ba8cf82aa352fca5e5a0fd34122.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >狼人和恶魔</h2>使用神圣的十字架、银器和火炬保护自己。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/fafda7ab9e0aa1c6af6e921ee566d369.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/fafda7ab9e0aa1c6af6e921ee566d369.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/fafda7ab9e0aa1c6af6e921ee566d369.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与你的同胞一起工作，战胜古老的邪灵。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/f052bd7af659c8d8d86c1567895c376a.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >清理村庄</h2>完成仪式并净化被邪恶困扰的村庄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/2caec4cd14f842191e6e4af4f6d25d19.poster.avif?t=1761870076\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/2caec4cd14f842191e6e4af4f6d25d19.webm?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844060/extras/2caec4cd14f842191e6e4af4f6d25d19.mp4?t=1761870076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重播能力</h2>要完成的目标是随机的。<br>门、仪式物品和收藏品是随机的。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >困难</h2>随着游戏的进行，黑暗肆虐并随着速度增加，试图阻止你的森林野兽也是如此。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >噩梦模式</h2>对于终极挑战，在村庄完全被黑暗吞噬之前，在有限的时间内完成地图。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏功能</h2>利用我们的游戏内定位语音聊天。带上朋友，或使用服务器浏览器寻找其他玩家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人玩家</h2>仅适用于铁杆玩家。自己做这一切。对于那些拥有最强信仰，因此有能力独自承担邪恶的人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告</h2>此游戏包含闪光灯，可能不适合患有光敏性癫痫或其他光敏状况的人。建议玩家自行决定。",
